data.description: Welcome to Camelot, a quaint neighborhood with No HOA. Nestled in the northeast this charming three-bedroom and two-bath 1 story ranch home is newly renovated and move in ready with great curb appeal.  Eat-in kitchen, and a grand main living room. No carpet, gorgeous neutral tile flooring through. Enter in the living room and enjoy the bright open floor plan.  Enjoy weekend BBQ time with family, friends and pets in your fenced in back patio.  Appreciate a large 2 car garage with plenty of space for lawn equipment. Newer HVAC, Fresh Paint, Updated Lighting, Plumbing Fixtures, foundation has been recently leveled and more. Come add your personal touch to this home. Easy access to I-35 and 410. Randolph AFB, Fort Sam Houston, Brooke Army Medical Center, Airport, the Quarry Market & Pearl within 15 -20 mins. Amazing, Eateries and Shopping, HEB, Walmart within 5 minutes. This home is a MUST SEE!!! Seller willing to assist with closing cost.
